  "text": "Another approach is for checking consistency of predefined interface processes [CITATION_1] . It is a useful method for bottom-up approaches to determine if these processes are interoperable for building a B2B scenario. Instead, our method promotes a topdown approach. Enterprises agree on an interaction global view and the behavioral constraints of each participant are guaranteed by deriving interface processes from a global interaction model.",
